<section id="heroSection">
    <h1>
        Elevate Your Style <br/> With Our <br id="mobileLineBreak"/> Affordable Luxury  <br/>  Braiding Service
    </h1>
    <h2>
        Plenty of braiding experience <br id="mobileLineBreak"/> to make you shine! <br/> Giving you a luxurious experience leaving you feeling gorgeous and confident.
    </h2>
    <div>
        <button> Book Appointment Now!</button>
        <p>Please read our <a href=""> Policy</a> and <a href=""> Location </a> info before booking</p>
